ults reveal that for efficient ISAC in\nwireless networks, energy-focused short-duration pulses are favorable for\nsensing while low-power long-duration signals are preferable for communication.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2022 17:32:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 29 Oct 2022 09:14:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 17:56:44 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 05:52:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
