ropose a software mapping scheme\nfor \\archname{} to further optimize the performance by fusing VMM and INV\ncrossbar. Experiment shows that \\archname{} can achieve an average of\n115.8$\\times$/11.4$\\times$ speedup and 41.9$\\times$/12.8$\\times$energy saving\ncompared to a GPU counterpart and PipeLayer on large-scale DNNs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2022 08:18:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-28"}
