en the downfall of Constantine VI and the\ncoronation of Charlemagne by contemporaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2022 11:11:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 09:32:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
