dia. The\nvolumetric gating will serve as an important addition to deep-tissue imaging\nmodalities and a useful tool for studying wave propagation in scattering media.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2022 02:16:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-07"}
